## Link Format Rules (Critically Important)

This page is located at `.doc-build/{{.CatalogDirPath}}/index.md`.

**All related links must use relative paths in the following format:**

1. Link to sibling pages under the same parent section: `../sibling-path/index.md`
   - Example: from `configuration/claude-config/` to `configuration/project-config/`
   - Write: `[Project Config](../project-config/index.md)`

2. Link to other top-level sections or their child pages: `../../other-section/index.md` or `../../other-section/child/index.md`
   - Example: from `configuration/claude-config/` to `core-modules/scanner/`
   - Write: `[Project Scanner](../../core-modules/scanner/index.md)`

3. Link to parent section's index: `../index.md`
   - Example: from `configuration/claude-config/` to `configuration/`
   - Write: `[Configuration](../index.md)`

**Absolutely forbidden link formats:**
- `(section.subsection)` — dot-notation
- `(section-name)` — missing path and index.md
- `(../section/)` — missing index.md
- `(generator/pipeline/)` — non-existent section name

